         ParsedExpression " If Trim(ClmCrfIn1.NTWK) = 'UNK' Then 0 Else  If Trim(ClmCrfIn1.NTWK) = 'NA' Then 1 Else  If (Len(Trim(ClmCrfIn1.NTWK)) = 0 and Trim(ClmCrfIn1.SRC_SYS_CD) = \"FACETS\") then GetFkeyNtwk(\"FACETS\", ClmCrfIn1.CLM_SK, \" \", Logging) else GetFkeyNtwk(\"FACETS\", ClmCrfIn1.CLM_SK, ClmCrfIn1.NTWK, Logging)"
