rker for the last set of records when the number is less than the specified transaction record count value\" label=\"End of data\" name=\"EndOfData\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/></Property></Property><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Transaction grouping allows operations on multiple links to be executed within a single transaction.\" engines=\"se\" inputLinkCountConstraint=\"multiple\" label=\"Enable transaction grouping\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"EnableTransactionGrouping\" required=\"false\" scope=\"stage\" specialFilter=\"1\" type=\"bool\"/><Property contexts=\"target\" description=\"Transaction grouping settings\" engines=\"se\" inputLinkCountConstraint=\"multiple\" label=\"Transaction grouping\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"TransactionGrouping\" required=\"false\" scope=\"link\" specialFilter=\"1\" type=\"category\"><Property default=\"0\" description=\"The action to be taken when a link is skipped\" label=\"Action on skip\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"ActionOnSkip\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Continue</Value><Value code=\"1\">Rollback</Value></Property><Property default=\"1\" description=\"The action to be taken when a failure occurs on a link\" label=\"Action on failure\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"ActionOnFailure\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Continue</Value><Value code=\"1\">Rollback</Value></Property></Property><Property description=\"Session properties\" label=\"Session\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"Session\" required=\"false\" scope=\"all\" type=\"category\"><Property default=\"1\" description=\"Specifies the isolation level that is used for all database transactions.\" label=\"Isolation level\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"IsolationLevel\" required=\"true\" scope=\"stage\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Read uncommitted</Value><Value code=\"1\">Cursor stability</Value><Value code=\"2\">Read stability