rrors that occur on individual partitions.\" label=\"Isolate partition errors\" name=\"IsolatePartErrors\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"><Value code=\"0\">Setup errors only</Value><Value code=\"1\">Load errors only</Value><Value code=\"2\">Setup and load errors</Value><Value code=\"3\">No isolation</Value></Property><Property default=\"100\" description=\"Specifies the number of megabytes of data to load before generating a progress message.\" label=\"Status interval\" maxValue=\"4000\" minValue=\"1\" name=\"StatusInterval\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the range of TCP ports that are used to create sockets for internal communications.\" filterChildPropertiesOnValue=\"true\" label=\"Port range\" name=\"PortRange\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"><Property description=\"Lower port number of the port range\" label=\"Lower port number\" maxValue=\"65535\" minValue=\"0\" name=\"MinValue\" required=\"true\" type=\"int\"/><Property description=\"Higher port number of the port range\" label=\"Higher port number\" maxValue=\"65535\" minValue=\"0\" name=\"MaxValue\" required=\"true\" type=\"int\"/></Property><Property default=\"false\" description=\"If selected, data records are checked for truncation at input and output.\" label=\"Check truncation\" name=\"CheckTruncation\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"0\" description=\"Specifies the number of records to trace in a dump of the data conversion process and the output of the hashing values.\" label=\"Trace\" minValue=\"0\" name=\"Trace\" required=\"false\" type=\"int\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the name of the partitioned distribution file.\" label=\"Partitioned distribution file\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"DistFile\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"/><Property default=\"false\" description=\"If selected, the partition map header is not included in the partition file.\" hidden=\"true\" label=\"Omit header\" name=\"OmitHeader\" required=