      Name "V0A7"
      NextID "0"
      AnnotationType "0"
      AnnotationText "This whole process of this reference lookup of claims is for the PCA claims which are coming in new as they don't exist in 'hf_clm' as it is cleared daily as the Fkey lookup fails and returns '0'. So we split the transformer for PCA_TYP_CD_SK <> 0 and PCA_TYP_CD_SK <> 1 and then reference lookup it on the MICRO_ID and then get the actual Base_Clm_Sk for the PCA claim."
